## Pomodoro timer\
- [ ] Ensure Pomodoro timer handles Pause/Resume correctly: pressing Pause freezes countdown, pressing Start resumes from remaining time, pressing Reset always returns to full session length. At 0, alarm plays and timer auto-switches to next phase. If user changes session length in Settings mid-countdown, update remaining time immediately based on elapsed; if paused, reset to new full duration. Require pressing Enter to confirm new time, ensuring alarm still triggers correctly at 0. Add option for phase transitions: by default, timer auto-starts the next phase (work \uc0\u8594  break \u8594  work), with a setting to require manual start for next phase so users can choose between seamless rhythm or manual control.\
\
